release: v0.2.0 — .harness/ unified layout + harness_uninstall + safe init defaults

BREAKING CHANGES
----------------
- All harness-owned artifacts moved into .harness/ (was scattered across project root,
  docs/, scripts/). CHANGELOG.md and .github/* preserved at root per external tool
  conventions. No fallback — old projects must migrate (see CHANGELOG migration guide).
  - harness.config.json            -> .harness/config.json
  - verification_baseline.json     -> .harness/baseline.json
  - docs/engineering-harness.md    -> .harness/engineering-harness.md
  - docs/adr/*                     -> .harness/adr/*
  - docs/features/*                -> .harness/features/*
  - engineering-check.{ps1,sh}     -> .harness/scripts/engineering-check.{ps1,sh}
  - docs/oncall.md | SLO.md | DORA.md | SBOM.md | rfc/* | compliance/.gitkeep
                                   -> all under .harness/
- harness_init now defaults to safe-keep: existing files whose content differs from
  template are reported as skipped(reason='kept_existing') instead of being overwritten.
  Pass force=true / CLI --force to opt into explicit regenerate.

ADDED
-----
- harness_uninstall: 7th MCP tool + matching CLI command. Recursively removes .harness/.
  Auto-preserves CHANGELOG.md and .github/* (external conventions). Supports
  --dry-run / --keep-root-dir / -y (skip confirmation).
- harness init --force: explicit overwrite flag for regeneration scenarios.
- src/core/paths.ts: single source of truth for all harness path constants.
- featureDirPath() / gateReviewPath() helpers.

CHANGED
-------
- 6 source modules (init / loader / runner / gate-review / upgrade / check) now consume
  HARNESS_PATHS constants; zero remaining bare path strings.
- 4 templates (engineering-harness.md.hbs, README.md.hbs, ADR baseline, feature templates)
  updated to .harness/* paths.
- 27 documentation files (README, docs/, assets/spec/, assets/templates/, assets/rules/)
  updated to reflect the new layout.

DOCS
----
- New: docs/COMPARISON.md — harness vs Cursor rules / Claude memories / Aider / Copilot
  WS / Custom Instructions, with 16-dimension comparison matrix + coexistence guide.
- New: docs/EXECUTION_FLOW.md — 9 mermaid sequence/flowchart diagrams covering all
  7 tools + modifier detection + end-to-end pipeline.
- README §2 rewritten as fully copy-paste-runnable 6-step quickstart with ASCII
  expected output blocks.

TESTS
-----
- 69 / 69 PASS across 14 files (up from 61 / 13 in 0.1.x).
- New init.test.ts cases: kept_existing default + force-overwrite.
- New uninstall.test.ts (6 cases): not_found / dry_run / actual cleanup / external
  artifact preservation / keep_root_dir / re-install lifecycle.

VERIFIED
--------
- npm run lint     : 0 errors, 0 warnings
- npm run typecheck: PASS
- npm test         : 69 / 69 PASS (1.97s)
- npm run build    : SUCCESS (cli 91.8KB / mcp-server 81.7KB / index 91.8KB / DTS 10.4KB)
- npm pack         : 492.1 kB tarball, 136 files, includes dist + assets + README + CHANGELOG + LICENSE
